Install voipmonitor dependencies
================================

emerge libpcap zlib

Install voipmonitor
===================

cd /path/to/voipmonitor
make clean
make
make install
cp config/voipmonitor.conf /etc/
cp config/init.d/voipmonitor /etc/init.d/

Edit the config file, prepare the mysql table and run voipmonitor


